Comment (src/views/admin/NotificationsView.vue:1330):
`autoRefreshJobs` starts a 30s interval that continues calling `loadJobs()` even when the user navigates away from the Deliveries tab (until they manually uncheck or unmount). This can generate unnecessary background traffic and overwrite the job list while viewing other tabs. Consider pausing the interval when `activeTab !== 'deliveries'` (e.g., watch `activeTab` to clear it, or guard inside the interval callback).

